@NODE Introduction "What are the AMOSPro GadTools?"

What are the AMOSPro GadTools?
------------------------------

The AMOSPro GadTools are an Include-File for AMOS Professional V2.00.
That is: You must link it with the 'Include'-Instruction of AMOSPro on your
Mainprogram. (Please read in addition to it also @{"Important !!!" LINK Important})
Then have you 34 Instructions for any GadGets. I have programing the GadTools
so that you have not only any Buttons, but also an complete Packet to create
very easy Screens & Masks that showing in the OS3.x Look. You can so very
easy Work.

@ENDNODE


